					<li class="text-green-600 underline">Manifesto (coming soon)</li>
					<li class="text-green-600 underline">Blog (coming soon)</li>
			</ul>
			<ul class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center items-center list-none space-y-4 sm:space-y-8">
